// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0036 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: f134c819-93cd-59be-82a7-f0be947f5978

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
